<br>
The other night I was at Kerra Island, working on improving my casting ability in quiet (nobody at all in that zone), and I had Rusty, my pet tiger, attacking Spikefish (and looking for Razortooth) while I was sitting on the boat medding.<br>
<br>
It didn't matter where he was, I either got a &quot;Attacking Spikefish&quot; or &quot;Sorry master, that is not a valid target&quot;.<br>
<br>
When it did say it was attacking, most of the time I never saw him fight, though I did see the taunting messages.  Though, I admit, it wasn't a very big zone and he may have been close to me (don't know, he was make believing he was a cat-fish).<br>
<br>
